com.hpe.caf.worker.document.model

Interface DocumentWorkerObject

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Application, BatchSizeController, Document, Documents, Failure, Failures, Field, Fields, FieldValue, FieldValues, HealthMonitor, InputMessageProcessor, Response, ResponseCustomData, ResponseQueue, Script, Scripts, ServiceLocator, Subdocument, Subdocuments, Task

    public interface DocumentWorkerObject
    This is the base object of the Document Worker Object Model. All object model interfaces derive from this interface. Any functionality added here is available from all object model objects.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Application getApplication()
      Returns the Application object, which represents the Document Worker itself.

    • Method Detail

      • getApplication

        @Nonnull
Application getApplication()
        Returns the Application object, which represents the Document Worker itself. This can be used to retrieve worker-scope details, such as configuration, access to the remote data store, etc.
        Returns:
        the root Application object
